      "problem": {
        "zh-TW": "進度資訊分散在多個系統，主管難以即時掌握。",
        "en-US": "Progress data was spread across multiple tools with low real-time visibility."
      },
      "solution": {
        "zh-TW": "建立 API 聚合層與可篩選 dashboard，支持角色化檢視。",
        "en-US": "Built an API aggregation layer and role-based filterable dashboards."
