      "id": "project-03",
      "slug": "clinic-intake-flow",
      "title": {
        "zh-TW": "門診報到流程優化",
        "en-US": "Clinic Intake Flow Optimization"
      },
      "summary": {
        "zh-TW": "重整門診報到流程與狀態邏輯，降低櫃檯溝通成本。",
        "en-US": "Refactored intake state transitions to reduce front-desk coordination overhead."
      },
      "problem": {
        "zh-TW": "病患狀態切換繁瑣，容易出現資料不同步。",
        "en-US": "Patient status transitions were brittle and often became inconsistent."
      },
      "solution": {
        "zh-TW": "建立狀態機模型並以可視化時間線呈現處理進度。",
        "en-US": "Built a state-machine model and visual timeline for processing stages."
      },
      "impact": [
        {
          "zh-TW": "櫃檯回報錯誤率下降 28%",
          "en-US": "Reduced front-desk reporting errors by 28%"
        }
      ],
